  Animal tiles are different sizes to emphasize their exhibit sizes


2. everyone manages portion of zoo
  Cooperative
  Reskin of takenoko
  Hex tiles are animal exhibits
  aqueducts are pathways for guests
  zookkeeper mini moves around to make animals breed/grow/happy




